{"tid":1191734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃台仰：支持港獨　仍認同以武制暴","createTime":"2019-06-08T05:40:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T05:49:11.000Z","uid":47714,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a0cee0caa939ece3c47b54b9db76483ac3cc257c","tid":1191734,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T05:40:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190606/59681537\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190606%2F59681537&d=Bm7f%2FS52JQW29R4IancW8%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=7b6107ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190606%2F59681537&h=b56f1b78\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190606/59681537</a><br />\n<br />\n本民前黃台仰和李東昇早前公開其難民身份後稱，現時不再提倡港獨。黃台仰接受《蘋果》專訪時否認不再支持港獨，「我係話唔提倡，唔代表唔支持」，並指至今仍認同「以武制暴」概念，「一直所講嘅以武制暴，係面對政權同警察嘅暴力，我哋要用番相應程度嘅力量去對抗」。"},{"pid":"aeffd139959d562aefeca7fdf96cd10c5e4daccf","tid":1191734,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T05:42:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"736e651a8a4ef0b7c99c983ede9dbf69e17b1dde","tid":1191734,"uid":52230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T05:46:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>槍口一致對外！<br />\n<br />\n不要分化，不要懷疑隊友！<br />\n<br />\n有人被捕立即集體救援！<br />\n<br />\n保護同伴！<br />\n<br />\n6.9 GOGOGO!</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe2e57d7db29cfd0e6c8af280df20a89cc93df2","tid":1191734,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T05:49:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}